      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliability. The engine starts up easily and the transmission shifts smoothly, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily commuter. While the interior is clean and well-kept, you may find some minor cosmetic wear on the upholstery and a few light surface scratches on the exterior, which are typical for its age. Overall, it is a solid, well-performing vehicle that is ready for the road without any immediate maintenance needs.",
