      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my ride. This car has been such a reliable companion for me, and it's still in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable, comfy vehicle that still looks great and drives smoothly, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
