      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape and ready for a new home! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs like a dream, and still has so much life left in it. It\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love driving it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 inline-six engine. This unit exhibits strong compression and linear power delivery through its six individual throttle bodies. Crucially, the double-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The drivetrain utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional tactile feedback. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers for improved damping characteristics and adjustable ride height. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearings and cooling system\u2014are in excellent health, making this a driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 32500.0,
